cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.ET, cs.EM, cs.ETM 

The paper discusses the development of a fully memristive neural network for image preprocessing and pattern recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves computer vision techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of memristors in the network implies that it could be categorized under cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), cs.EM (Electromagnetics), or cs.ETM (Emerging Technologies in Measurement).
